<p id=3D"cb0c19ba-848c-4c92-bf3c-1a16cf69d1a2">The number phi, often known =
as the golden ratio, is a mathematical concept that people have known about=
 since the time of the ancient Greeks. It is an irrational number like <a d=
ata-analytics-id=3D"inline-link" href=3D"https://www.livescience.com/29197-=
what-is-pi.html" data-mrf-recirculation=3D"inline-link" data-before-rewrite=
