-hl-processed=3D"none" data-hawk-tracked=3D"hawklinks"><u>pi</u></a> and e,=
 meaning that its terms go on forever after the decimal point without repea=
ting.&nbsp;</p><div id=3D"ad-unit-1" class=3D"ad-unit"></div><p>Over the ce=
nturies, a great deal of lore has built up around phi, such as the idea tha=
t it represents perfect beauty or is uniquely found throughout nature. But =
much of that has no basis in reality.&nbsp;</p><div class=3D"jwplayer__widt=
hsetter" id=3D"tQStZJka">
<div class=3D"jwplayer__wrapper">
<div id=3D"futr_botr_tQStZJka_UbKkvo80_div" class=3D"future__jwplayer" data=
